        {
          "name": "region",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "The expected physical location at the time of the App Clip’s invocation."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "completionHandler",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "A closure called when the platform confirms the expected physical location at the time of the App Clip’s invocation."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "The closure takes the following parameters:"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "termList",
              "items": [
                {
                  "term": {
                    "inlineContent": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "inRegion"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "definition": {
                    "content": [
                      {
                        "type": "paragraph",
                        "inlineContent": [
                          {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": "A Boolean value that indicates whether the App Clip’s invocation happened at the expected physical location."
                          }
                        ]
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                },
                {
                  "term": {
                    "inlineContent": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "error"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "definition": {
                    "content": [
                      {
                        "type": "paragraph",
                        "inlineContent": [
                          {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": "The error object that describes why the platform couldn’t confirm the user’s physical location."
                          }
                        ]
                      },
                      {
                        "type": "paragraph",
                        "inlineContent": [
                          {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": "This parameter is "
                          },
                          {
                            "type": "codeVoice",
                            "code": "nil"
                          },
                          {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": " if the platform was able to determine the user’s physical location at the time of the App Clip’s invocation."
                          }
                        ]
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Confirm the user’s location at the time of the App Clip’s invocation if the App Clip is associated with a physical location. The request to confirm the location fails with "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/app_clips/apactivationpayloaderror/3585118-disallowed"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " if the source of the invocation isn’t an NFC tag or visual code."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "For the platform to accept the request to confirm the user’s location, you need to make modifications to the App Clip’s "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "Info.plist"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " file. For more information, see "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/app_clips/enabling_notifications_in_app_clips"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "aside",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Functionality to confirm the user’s location is only available to App Clips. For your App Clip’s corresponding full app, request permission to access the user’s location and make use of the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/corelocation"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " framework. For more information, see "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/corelocation/getting_the_user_s_location"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "."
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "style": "note",
          "name": "Note"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": []
        }
      ]
